# Never upload local env files to Vercel builds.
# Production config comes from the Vercel project's Environment Variables
# (VITE_AUTH_MODE=cookie, VITE_API_BASE=https://api.umiconsulting.co, VITE_SUPABASE_*).
# Shipping the local-dev .env (VITE_AUTH_MODE=local, no VITE_API_BASE) is what
# previously broke the prod build into same-origin/supabase mode.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
